The paper deals with resource allocation in cloud computing, which is a topic that falls under several sub-categories in computer science. Game theory (cs.GT) is a likely category since the paper discusses pricing mechanisms and competitive ratios. Distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) is also a possible category since the paper deals with resource allocation in a cloud computing platform. Data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) is another possible category since the paper discusses the design of pricing functions. Other possible categories include computer systems and networking (cs.CC) and systems and control (cs.SY).
